content: 蔡英文在元旦祝词中用了这样一段话：我要把台湾打造成为一个团结而有公义的社会，这样的政府不会用推土机辗过人民的土地；不会用白色恐怖的手段来对付政敌；不会将公共资源私相授受；不会用金钱和政治力来控制媒体。也不会牺牲人权来换取短期的利益...
content_translated: In its New Year's message, Choi English used the phrase: I want to make Taiwan a united and just society, a government that does not run over people's land with bulldozers; does not use white terror against political opponents; does not provide private access to public resources; and does not control the media with money and political power. And not to sacrifice human rights for short-term benefit...

content: 【射手坐怎样克服相爱距离】异地恋中的任何阻碍都能被TA看成对真爱的考验，并且TA也有信心通过这些阻碍。最重要的是异地恋能给TA最喜爱的自由，可以恋爱，也可以有自己的小天地。应该多用关心的态度去了解远在他方的射手的生活状况，过得不好就要多给予关心和帮助，若是过得太逍遥就要多给些提醒。
content_translated: Any obstacle in a foreign relationship can be seen by TA as a test of true love, and TA is confident that it will pass. The most important thing is that exotic love gives the TA's favorite freedom to fall in love and have its own little world. More care should be taken to understand the living conditions of shooters far from home, more care and help if they are to live too far away, and more warning if they are to go too far.

content: 云南普洱茶是云南的名茶，古今中外负有盛名，它以西双版纳地区仅有的滇青毛茶为原料,普洱茶的历史十分悠久，早在唐代就有普洱茶的贸易了。普洱茶采用的是优良品质的云南大叶种茶树之鲜叶，分为春、夏、秋三个。春茶有分为“春尖”、“春中”、“春尾”三个等级；夏茶又称“二水”；秋茶又称为“谷花”
content_translated: Yunnan Pu Ma tea is the famous tea of Yunnan, and it is based on the only fluncing tea in the Western Twina region, which has a long history and traded as far back as Tang Dynasty. Pu-Ma tea is used as a Quality Yunnan Leaf of Tea Trees, divided into spring, summer and autumn. Spring tea is divided into “spring”, “spring”, “springtail”; summer tea is also called “two water”; and autumn tea is also known as “valow flowers”.

content: 开始让一些人渐渐淡出我的生活。你不是我的，我亦不是你的。我的心那么小，可以遇见的人不多，可以付出的，亦只有那么几个。记忆里残存的温柔，终会抵不过眼前平时的幸福。哪怕它，只是一个小小的光点，所以，我们亦只能看见眼前，然后简单的生活，区别的，只是心而已。
content_translated: It's starting to get some people out of my life. You're not mine and I'm not yours. My heart is so small, there are few people I can meet, and there are only a few. And the tenderness that remains in the memory will not be more than the happiness that is present. Even if it's just a little light, so we can only see the eyes, then simple life, different, just the heart.

content_translated: The words of wisdom: anger is to punish oneself with the wrongs of others; distress is to torment oneself with the wrongs of others; regret is to destroy oneself with the helpless past; fear is to frighten oneself with a virtual risk; loneliness is to restrain oneself with a homemade cell; and debase oneself with the strength of others. It'll be easier for you to leave it behind!

content: 老北京面馆最大特色就是吆喝。有天两人去吃面，跑堂吆喝上了：“5号桌，炸酱面两碗”吃完结帐，共25元8毛。甲说：“给你26，别找了”跑堂接过钱便吆喝：“5号桌有客送小费2毛”满大厅的人回头看他，甲脸红了：“得，那2毛你还是找我吧 ”跑堂又吆喝上了：“5号桌的2毛小费又要回去了!”
content_translated: The biggest feature of the old Beijing noodle shop is sip. One day, two people went to eat noodles and ran and drank: “Table 5, two bowls of fried noodles” and settled the account for 25 cents. And A says, "Here's 26, don't find the money, and drink it up." "Turn table 5 has a tip for 2 cents." The people in the lobby look back, and they look red, and they say, "Oh, well, that's 20 cents for me."

So that, as Luxur said, a fireplace would bleed. People never want revolution, they never call for change. It was the rulers who chose revolution without reform. The “good-bye revolution” is a hypocritical proposition. Because the people have been trying to say goodbye to the revolution. Don't talk to the people about the revolution, have the guts to talk to the queen.

content: 哈哈，知道您忙么。牙买加是个国际旅游目的地，特别是欧美人很喜欢去。该国的旅游部长我比较熟，那里投资旅游度假酒店非常棒。另外，我几个哥们想在首都金斯敦搞一个中国城和一个类似于唐宁街的中国商业街，同时收购牙买加蓝山咖啡的几个庄园，不知道您有兴趣吗？
content_translated: Ha ha, know you're busy. Jamaica is an international tourist destination, particularly for the European and American peoples. content: 【六招让孩子不黏电视】寒假到了，许多孩子喜欢“挂”在电视前，不但对眼睛不利，体智脑的发育也受到影响。预防6招——1.事先订好看电视规则；2.用好的DVD取代不好的电视节目；3.把电视和遥控器藏起来；4.别在孩子的房间放电视；5.别把电视当保姆；6.家长要以身作则，创造更多家庭活动。
content_translated: It's a cold break for kids who like to hang up on TV, not only to the detriment of their eyes but also to the development of their mental and intellectual capacities. Prevention of 6 moves - 1. Pre-ordering of good-looking television rules; 2. Replacement of bad television programmes with good DVDs; 3. Hide television and remote controls; 4. Do not put television in children's rooms; 5. Do not use television as a nanny; 6. Parents should lead by example in creating more family activities.

content: 看《霍金的宇宙》，我的论断是：人类永远也不可能实现“时间旅行”。证据就是：我们的生活中，没有出现从未来来的人。“时间旅行”或者是人类技术的极限，或者是人类寿命的局限。如果是前者，则证明了科学有末日；如果是后者，则证明了人类有末日。
content_translated: Looking at Hawking's Universe, my assertion is that humans can never achieve “time travel”. The proof is that there is no future in our lives. “Time travel” is either the limit of human technology or the limit of human lifetime. In the case of the former, there is proof of the end of science; in the case of the latter, there is proof of the end of humanity.
